Introduction

Im YeoJin is a South Korean singer-songwriter under CTDENM. She is the maknae and center of the girl group Loossemble. She is also the maknae of the girl group LOONA, and its sub-unit LOONA 1/3.

She released her solo single album “YeoJin” on January 16, 2017. She debuted in LOONA on August 20, 2018, with their debut mini album “[+ +]”. However, she parted ways with BlockBerryCreative after a legal dispute.

On June 11, 2023, it was announced that she signed an exclusive contract with CTDENM. On July 29, It was also confirmed that she would debut as a member of Loossemble alongside some of the other members of her former group. On September 15th, 2023, she debuted as a member of Loossemble with a mini album of the same name.
